com.att.aro.model
Class TCPSession

java.lang.Object
  com.att.aro.model.TCPSession
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<TCPSession>
public class TCPSession
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<TCPSession>

Represents a TCP session, acting as a bean class for session information. Provides methods for extracting a list of sessions from a collection of packets, and analyzing a session to retrieve the TCP information.

See Also:
